@startuml
title Gestion des formations

actor Visiteur as V
actor Proprietaire as Auth
boundary Front as F
control API as API
database BD as BD

== Consultation (publique) ==
V -> F: Navigation page compétences / profil
F -> API: GET /api/formations
note right: Accès libre
API -> BD: SELECT * FROM formations ORDER BY ordre, date_debut DESC
BD --> API: Liste des formations
API --> F: JSON [{diplome, etablissement, ...}]
F --> V: Affichage formations

== Gestion (authentifié) ==
Auth -> F: Dashboard formations
F -> API: GET /api/formations
note right: Proprietaire uniquement
API -> BD: SELECT ...
BD --> API: Liste complète
API --> F: JSON
F --> Auth: Formulaire de gestion

Auth -> F: Ajouter une formation
F -> API: POST /api/formations {diplome, etablissement, ...}
note right: Auth requis (Bearer token)
API -> BD: INSERT INTO formations
BD --> API: Nouvelle formation
API --> F: 201 Created
F --> Auth: Confirmation

Auth -> F: Modifier une formation
F -> API: PUT /api/formations/{id} {diplome, ...}
API -> BD: UPDATE formations
BD --> API: Formation modifiée
API --> F: 200 OK
F --> Auth: Confirmation

Auth -> F: Supprimer une formation
F -> API: DELETE /api/formations/{id}
API -> BD: DELETE FROM formations
BD --> API: OK
API --> F: 204 No Content
F --> Auth: Confirmation
@enduml
